        public java.lang.String getDetectedInBuild()
        Getter
        Returns:
        the build label assigned to the scan in which this issue was detected first time. If the issue was fixed and reintroduced, this value will hold the build label where it was reintroduced last. Will be null if scans have not been tagged with build labels or if issue has been present in all scans
